  drop_na(diet.diversity) %>% 
  split(.$size) %>% 
  map(~lm(diet.diversity ~ cover.diversity, data=.x)) %>% 
  map(summary) %>% 
  map(glance) %>% 
  bind_rows(.id='size') 
```
Diet diversity ~ landcover edge density
```{r}
# The diversity of the diet is determined by land cover edge density.
