  drop_na(diet.diversity) %>% 
  split(.$size) %>% 
  map(~lm(diet.diversity ~ cover.edge.density, data=.x)) %>% 
  map(summary) %>% 
  map(glance) %>% 
  bind_rows(.id='size') 
```

Diet diversity ~ landcover interspersion
```{r}
# The diversity of the diet is determined by land cover interspersion.
